                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17281204-33-victim210 t17281204-33-viclabel149"></join>; on the <rs id="t17281204-33-cd150" type="crimeDate">21st of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17281204-33-off148 t17281204-33-cd150"></join> in the Night time, and stealing thence one Dozen of Silver hafted Knives, one Dozen of Silver Hafted Forks, two Silver Salvers, a Pepper Box, a Milk Pot, a Silver Boat, and several other pieces of Silver Furniture, besides a Cloak, a piece of Shagreen, and other Goods, the Property of the said 
